    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s still got plenty of zip? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really great shape, super clean inside, and runs like a dream. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to hit the road with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
