      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This high-revving engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering the telepathic feedback and turn-in response characteristic of this legendary platform. A well-preserved specimen for the purist seeking analog performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minor cosmetic scratches. Full service history available. Runs well.",
      "price": 31500.0,
