      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been so reliable for me over the years! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, it\u2019s a smooth, comfy ride that\u2019s been well-loved and looked after. I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
