      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 high-revving inline-six. This specimen retains its original Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, providing crisp engagement. Mechanically, the Double VANOS system is operational and the subframe has been inspected for common structural fatigue issues associated with the chassis. It sits on a factory-spec suspension with refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and balanced 50/50 weight distribution remain intact. The limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up under load. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and the individual throttle bodies offer instantaneous throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
